	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, GUI tools are fine for one-off conversions, but what if you want to tweak something at the beginning and do all the conversion steps again? Oh, and again after making another change? GUIs are about manually doing things over and over, making little errors or not doing it exactly the same each time. Inferior.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


