		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Then you can write a batch file, shell script, or makefile that does the conversion steps for you and runs the result in an emulator. The way I have had my environment set up since sometime in 2009, it's as simple as edit, Ctrl+S, Ctrl+R, listen, close emulator.

		

		</td>
